# ShiftCrew Waiter — environment
# These point at the shared ShiftMatch Supabase project. The waiter app has NO
# login: access is granted purely by whether the phone number is on the owner's
# roster. It only ever reads its OWN isolated schemas (shiftcrew_waiter for the
# published menu + leaderboard, shiftcrew_owner for the waiter_access roster RPC).
# It never touches ShiftMatch's public data.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
